  "contentHtml": "<!-- BEGIN COPYRIGHTED TEXT CHUNK --><html><head></head><body><div class=\"chapter\">\n\n\n<h1>Basics</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/faq\">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/begin\">Beginnings</a> — good starting points for newcomers to this site</li>\n<li><a href=\"/tech/download/bulk\">Download the whole website</a> — step-by-step instructions</li>\n<li><a href=\"/devices\">ATI on many devices</a> (offline edition, iPads, iPhones, more...)</li>\n<!-- \n<li><a href=\"http://www.accesstoinsight.org/rss/news.rss.php\">Subscribe to Access to Insight via RSS feed</a> &mdash; keeping up-to-date with changes and additions to the website</li>\n -->\n<li><a href=\"/abbrev\">Abbreviations and symbols</a> that are used throughout the website</li>\n<li><a href=\"/glossary\">Glossary of Pali and Buddhist Terms</a> appearing in many texts offered here</li>\n<li>Biographical notes about the <a href=\"/authors\">contributing authors and translators</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/random-sutta\">Random sutta</a> | <a href=\"/random-article\">random article</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"chapter\">\n<h1><a id=\"map\">Site Map</a></h1>\n<table class=\"help1\">\n\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t<td class=\"cat_heading\">Getting help : </td>\n\t\t<td class=\"cat_list\">\n\t\t\t– <a href=\"/faq\">Frequently Asked Questions about Access to Insight</a><br>\n\t\t\t– <a href=\"/glossary\">Glossary</a><br>\n\t\t\t– <a href=\"/abbrev\">Abbreviations, symbols, and sutta numbering schemes</a><br>\n\t\t\t– How to download: <a href=\"/tech/download\">files</a> | <a href=\"/tech/download/bulk\">the entire website</a><br></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td class=\"cat_heading\">Finding things : </td>\n\t\t<td class=\"cat_list\">\n\t\t\t– <a href=\"/search_results\">Search engine</a><br>\n\t\t\t– Indexes: <a href=\"/index-subject\">General</a> | <a href=\"/index-author\">Author</a> | <a href=\"/index-title\">Title</a> | <a href=\"/index-sutta\">S